text: Boroneddu (Boronèddu) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 149 people lived there. Its area is 4.59 km². It is 206 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
title: Boroneddu
